content: Jianchao Li is a software engineer specialized in deep learning, machine learning and computer vision. He is working at Facebook in Zurich, Switzerland now. Previously, he has been working at Indeed in Tokyo, Japan, ByteDance AI Lab in Beijing, China, and ViSenze in Singapore.
